column5: Heard ramblings from two of my friends that hwy 11 will be closed this weekend in Hunstville.  Any truth to this?   I have looked and looked and the only thing I see is that Hwy 60 will be closed in sections around Deerhurst.  Leaving fro Nipissing tomorrow and don't want to get stuck somewhere.  THanks.
Just came back from Toronto today....POLICE PRESENCE!!!!  I've never seen so many cruisers in my life all the way from BPS to Huntsville and beyond.  but the only closure was Hwy 60.  Randy
